data.description: Wonderful one owner home available only due to transfer. This property is meticulously cared for and still has future lower level expansion possible. Bright open main floor with breakfast area, snack bar counter, formal dining, family room with fireplace and two story solarium with overlooking balcony. Upper bedrooms are generous in size and there is a full Jack and Jill bath. In addition to the beautifully maintained newly landscaped yard with picturesque spruce trees there is a three car attached and two car detached garage and both are heated for year found use. See supplement with many upgrades and features the Seller has completed.  Property is included in the Lake Riley Home Owners Association. Annual dues presently 200.00. Members have use of the beach area and there are a limited number of dock spaces available by lottery for association members. See attached Covenants.
